description:
This dataset locates all the Smoothie King locations across the USA as 12.2008. The information comes from their website at smoothieking.com. The data includes: address, city, state, zip, phone, and lat/lon location. The lat/lon location was obtained through the use of a geocoder at batchgeocode.com. 

To note: The locate a store service on smoothie king's website also listed locations that are pending and opening soon. These locations were not included because insufficient information was provided for their exact locations.
